column5: Gotta love life-proof cases. Run it over with the truck a few times and it will still work like new.

Cool  I dropped a $175.00 St croix and reel in 15' of water in the summer  Went back 2 weeks later and had my trail on the GPS. I hooks a bottom bouncer and 3 sets of J plug hooks on another rod and dragged the bottom. It was all sand so pretty easy. First pass I feel weight..yessss...bring it up and there is my outfit..gotta love GPS tracks
Gotta love life-proof cases. Run it over with the truck a few times and it will still work like new.  The S5 is waterproof from the factory.
lifeproof also has a floater lifejacket case, best $25 I've spent on phone accessories
